{
  "stem": "3631.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I think my father worked in the kitchen a little while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I worked up in Schindler's office-- not in-- not in the German office, but in Schindler's factory office civilian.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I expected to do some paperwork and typing and so on, but it's not what I did.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They made me a cost accountant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to do cost accountancy [CHUCKLES] for a product that we never really manufactured.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGH] So it was sort of a-- sort of a job-- an easy job I suppose.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But, again, you were always the-- the German guards-- they had quarters right in back of our office.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we always had to-- we heard when they had to march and sing-- march around in there and sing these Nazi songs.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and there was a German commander, a Sturmfuhrer Leopold, like a Captain Leopold, who was in charge there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I think Schindler had him-- Schindler arranged, just when it came to the end of the war, that he was transferred out of this-- out of Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that got him out of the way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as I said, prisons have no walls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a radio mechanic, a Jewish radio mechanic, who repaired the radios for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, we had no radios.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when he had to repair radios-- the German army, three times a day, gave out an army report status-- where they were.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Since I knew good German, and knew a lot about Germany, and I knew German shorthand, I took these reports down as well as I can.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I showed it to the other here, there, here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the word spread around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew what went on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "For instance, I came from Dresden.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
